data.description: Fantastic new price for this grand Victorian home.  It has been lovingly maintained and updated, while retaining its historical charm and detailing.  Over 2,300 square feet of living space PLUS a full walk-up attic AND a basement workshop area.  Outdoor patio spaces are ideal for morning coffee and breakfast, or enjoying the serenity of the koi pond at the end of your day.   The yards are beautifully landscaped.  Wrought iron fencing adds to the period authenticity.  Ideally located, it's a 10 minute walk to Russian River Brewing Company and many other shops and restuarants.
